Fixes BUG 446084 --- check for updates dialog is broken.

	  * Button labels contained characters "<" and ">", but should
	  instead contain the respective HTML entities, &lt; and &gt.
	  This patch corrects the problem, possibly leading to the solution
	  of other dependent bugs.	  

Approved by l10n@mozilla.com, see:
https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=446084#c11
